{"tid":2222201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"懲教拒披露口罩去向 立場投訴成立","createTime":"2020-09-29T02:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T03:15:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9916e6ff868ebb879c4ee1fce63d238a77e0077b","tid":2222201,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:45:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200929/BFUGFNJ73JENZMDH4YOU5PZPQE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200929%2FBFUGFNJ73JENZMDH4YOU5PZPQE%2F&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=21ddae75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200929%2FBFUGFNJ73JENZMDH4YOU5PZPQE%2F&h=618ac550\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200929/BFUGFNJ73JENZMDH4YOU5PZPQE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n懲教拒披露口罩去向 立場投訴成立<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Fk2-mDyW_ZM70Sf4TYQqYje3fEA=/1181x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DDLJADXXJZF53LPXEMDYAOTZUA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFk2-mDyW_ZM70Sf4TYQqYje3fEA%3D%2F1181x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDDLJADXXJZF53LPXEMDYAOTZUA.jpg&h=349364cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■懲教署生產的CSi口罩多次流出民間，令大眾質疑是否有人轉售圖利。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今年初武漢肺炎爆發，全港鬧口罩荒，懲。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n立場新聞昨報道，今年2月透過《公開資料守則》向懲教署索取CSi資料，包括獲分配口罩的非政府組織名單，但懲教署僅用110字簡略回覆，亦無提供名單。立場記者2月中多次致電懲教署公開資料主任，但從來沒人接聽電話，只好以電郵查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n申訴署僅建議吸取教訓<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，懲教署3月初始以電郵回覆立場記者，稱正就申請索取資料徵詢法律意見，至3月27日再回覆指索取的資料涉及第三者，所以未能提供。立場向申訴專員公署投訴後，懲。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n立場引述申訴專員回覆指已完成調查，確認投訴成立。調查發現懲教署職員沒按《公開資料守則》規定行事，情況不理想，但懲教署4月已作出補救。公署建議懲教署吸取教訓，確保嚴格按守則的要求行事。<br />\n<br />\n本報昨就報道向懲教署查詢，至截稿未獲回覆。《公開資料守則》規定，政府部門處理索取資料申請，處理時間不應超過51天。《鏗鏘集》團隊2月初亦引用《守則》向懲教署及物流署查詢CSi口罩去向被拒，申訴專員上月中亦裁定懲教署違反《守則》。"},{"pid":"7db294869ef6bebc068ea59cb7351aec048746a5","tid":2222201,"uid":119729,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"柳記根本同黑警一擔擔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"472e02716be47c5ab091ec6b3389de1622cc4aa7","tid":2222201,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:48:13.000Z","msg":"係人都知拎哂出去賣啦，1-2月果期缺口罩但係見到D廢老都有CSI戴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acdf38a8fc47690f2fdce915581eb3a4efc2a560","tid":2222201,"uid":62060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7db294869ef6bebc068ea59cb7351aec048746a5","tid":2222201,"uid":119729,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"柳記根本同黑警一擔擔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:50:13.000Z","msg":"柳記根本係連黑狗都不如嘅坐監狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人哋都叫做陀下炮出嚟打9人，人工又低人一截<br />\n柳記返入去陪犯坐監啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4a419ddebf1eb4e87cc43f1e961004d66f9bfd","tid":2222201,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acdf38a8fc47690f2fdce915581eb3a4efc2a560","tid":2222201,"uid":62060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7db294869ef6bebc068ea59cb7351aec048746a5","tid":2222201,"uid":119729,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"柳記根本同黑警一擔擔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:50:13.000Z","msg":"柳記根本係連黑狗都不如嘅坐監狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人哋都叫做陀下炮出嚟打9人，人工又低人一截<br />\n柳記返入去陪犯坐監啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202